Overlay dirs
============

1. The common/*/* will be automatically installed.

2. The rootfs/*/* will be automatically installed into the root filesystem.

3. The <OS>/*/* will be automatically installed into the target OS (including recovery, etc.).

4. Set RK_ROOTFS_EXTRA_OVERLAY_DIRS to specify custom rootfs overlay directories.

5. Unset RK_ROOTFS_OVERLAY to disable rootfs overlays.

6. Unset RK_OVERLAY to disable all overlays.

If an install.sh script exists in the overlay directory, it will be executed instead of the default rsync installation.
